Open the index.html file to play.

Tested in current versions of Chrome, Safari, and Firefox. Internet Explorer 9
also works with the exception of fullscreen support.




Instructions

Collect all red squares. Do not go offscreen.

Controls

Movement
W, A, S, D
Fullscreen
F

Planned Features

The red squares will be dynamically continously generated and the game will be
infinite. Score will be based on time. The camera will follow the needed
sequence of blocks. If either the player goes off screen or misses a block, the
game ends.